Interface Network.Update

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Appliable<Network>, Indexable, Network.UpdateStages.WithAddressSpace, Network.UpdateStages.WithDnsServer, Network.UpdateStages.WithSubnet, Resource.UpdateWithTags<Network.Update>
    Enclosing interface:
    Network

    public static interface Network.Update
extends Appliable<Network>, Resource.UpdateWithTags<Network.Update>, Network.UpdateStages.WithSubnet, Network.UpdateStages.WithDnsServer, Network.UpdateStages.WithAddressSpace
    The template for a public IP address update operation, containing all the settings that can be modified.

    Call Appliable.apply() to apply the changes to the resource in Azure.
